#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ Bank statement import
# GESBSIMTC
########################################################################################################################
# Updates       :
# Date          | Author | Version | Description
# 2016-10-11    | Bader  | U11     | LIENS, AM_DUDSEL, AM_BSIPAYCUR, AM_BSIDEPCUR:
#               |        |         | calc TOTAMT/TOTDEP using abs(BSIPAYCUR/BSIDEPCUR) instead of BSIPAYCUR/BSIDEPCUR
# 2016-10-13    | DNE    | U11     | x3-3984: In state "AD" manual selection must be not available.
# 2016-10-25    | Bader  | U11     | X3-4110: show payment reference
# 2016-10-28    | Bader  | U11     | X3-6247: LIENS: show bank sign from local menu 3680 instead of SNS (C/D/RC/RD)
# 2016-11-03    | Bader  | U11     | X3-6243: LIENS/AM_DUDSEL/AM_BSIPAYCUR/AM_BSIDEPCUR: support new field BSISNS
# 2016-11-11    | Bader  | U11_01  | X3-1501: Implementation of search term list
# 2016-11-22    | Bader  | U11_01  | X3-7660: Use new field BSITRS instead of SUP1 as link in PAYMENTH
# 2017-01-19    | Bader  | U11_02  | SAM 120988 Reset all filters
# 2017-01-24    | Bader  | U11_02  | SAM 121111 SETBOUT: refresh left list (otherwise empty in first entry of function)
# 2017-01-26    | Bader  | U11_02  | SAM 121111 revert change of 2017-01-24 because of refresh problems
# 2017-02-20    | Bader  | U11_03  | X3-26060: Suppress validation and matching if "Save" button active
# 2017-02-24    | Bader  | U11_03  | X3-26060: Replace Wrnbox by Infbox
# 2017-03-31    | DNE    | V11.0.4 | X3-31746: Restriction to a single BP removed.
# 2017-04-04    | angre  | V11.0.4 | X3-30338: Presentation of subdetail information
# 2017-04-05    | DNE    | V11.0.4 | X3-30338: Grid column naming in a dynamic way.
# 2017-05-02    | angre  | V11.0.4 | X3-33376: Disable overpayment when multiple BP in selected open items
# 2017-05-05    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35704: re-open showing of and tunneling to payment for B and C matches
# 2017-05-08    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35704: Add AVANT_SUITE for tunneling to multiple payments
# 2017-05-12    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35653: support FLGCRE = 3/4 (partially validated, manually closed > new local menu 3690)
# 2017-05-12    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35653: Add new function BSICLOTRS
# 2017-05-16    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35653: use new message text 218 instead of 216 after conflict resolution
# 2017-05-17    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35694: BUILD_PAYMENT_ARRAY: handle AS/AD matches like B/C matches (no open items matched)
# 2017-05-31    | Bader  | 2017.R3 | X3-35694: BUILD_PAYMENT_ARRAY: dim of arrays = rowcnt + 1 otherwise endless loop
# 2017-07-11    | angre  | 2017.R3 | X3-42425: BSI payment in currency
# 2017-08-09    | angre  | 2017.R4 | X3-47569: Modify controls for AC and BC flags
# 2017-08-17    | DNE    | 2017.R5 | X3-52272: BSIIMPPAR.FLGCLS: React on this flag with another message.
# 2017-08-21    | DNE    | 2017.R5 | X3-53026: Revision of BSIMTC calculation rules
# 2017-09-06    | DNE    | 2017.R5 | X3-53532: Blocking message, in case of overpayment in currency
# 2017-09-21    | DNE    | 2017.R3 | X3-55850: Support statement header status 'Reconcile'
# 2017-12-20    | DNE    | 2018.R1 | X3-68766: Make BSI robust if sales or purchase module is not available
# 2018-06-27    | DNE    | V12     | X3-96717: Meke the GESBSIMTC function working with new responsive UI
# Issue X3-109897 - 2018-10-09 by SEMOL : BAI originator ID hidded when it's not BAI2 format type
# 2018-11-13    | Bader  | 2018.R? | X3-103296: new grid for matched payments
# 2018-12-12    | Bader  | 2018.R? | X3-120227: SETBOUT: activate/deactivate manual payment search
# 2019-01-15    | Bader  | 2019.R? | X3-119483: manual entries for "AM" matches with payments
# 2019-02-01    | Bader  | 2019.R2 | X3-121978: init new "Matching type" field TYPMTC
# 2019-02-06    | Bader  | 2019.R2 | X3-119504: move open item grid + totals from screen BSIMTC0 to BSIMTC4
# 2019-03-18    | Bader  | 2019.R2 | X3-128734: make sure payment sign fits to transaction sign
# 2019-05-13    | Bader  | 2019.R3 | X3-139982: AM_DUDSEL: handle correctly open items in foreign currency
# 2019-07-31    | Bader  | 2019.R4 | X3-150002: LIENS: show fields MTCDATSTR and MTCDATEND
# 2019-08-14    | Bader  | 2019.R4 | X3-156158: SHOW_HIDE_TOTALS: Handling of currencies with 3 decimals
# 2019-09-04    | Bader  | 2019.R5 | X3-157415: APRES_MOD: set TMPCUR/TMPLOC in GACCDUDATE in case of update
# 2019-09-13    | Bader  | 2019.R5 | X3-160548: AM_DUDSEL: take into account the discount for calculation of DUDPAYCUR if statement currency <> OI currency
# 2019-11-12    | Bader  | 2020.R1 | X3-166778 RELBANK bridging - Create RELBANK entries
# 2019-11-27    | Bader  | 2020.R1 | X3-166805 RELBANK bridging - show/hide field "Reconciled"
# 2020-04-23    | Bader  | 2020.R3 | X3-192964 AM_DUDSEL: take care of partially paid OIs for calculation of DUDPAYCUR
# 2020-06-02    | Bader  | 2020.R3 | X3-200184 APRES_MOD: update [F:DUD] also if OI not selected (might have been de-selected)
#               |        |         | AM_DUDSEL, AM_DUDPAYCUR, AM_BSIDEPCUR, AM_DUDPAYSTM: update new balance field for remaining amount
#               |        |         | C_DUDPAYSTM: show blocking message only when OI and statement currency are the same (currency variance might need overpayment)
# 2020-06-08    | Bader  | 2020.R3 | X3-200184 APRES_MOD: update [F:DUD] calculate paid amount in company currency from amount in statement currency (not from OI currency)
# 2020-07-31    | Bader  | 2020.R4 | X3-208761 AVANT_OUVRE: check if statement has at least one transaction
# 2020-09-21    | Bader  | 2020.R4 | X3-215229 LIENS: make sure the correct grid (OIs or payments) is open for edit depending on matching status
# 2020-09-23    | Bader  | 2021.R1 | X3-211540: allow different payment sign for manual entries with payment matching (to handle transaction amount < payment amount)
# 2020-11-13    | Bader  | 2021.R1 | X3-223301 C_DUDSEL: add check if OI already selected in another transaction;
#               |        |         |           C_PAYSEL (new): add check if payment already selected in another transaction
# 2020-11-16    | Bader  | 2021.R1 | X3-224026: APRES_MOD: update [F:DUD]TMPLOC also when transaction currency = OI currency (regression X3-200184)
# 2020-11-27    | Bader  | 2021.R1 | X3-224555: add controls AS_DUDPAYCUR, AS_DUDPAYSTM, AS_BSIDEPCUR : don't allow entering values to open item grid if line is not ticked
# 2020-11-30    | Bader  | 2021.R1 | X3-225351: SETBOUT: correct enabling disabling of "Manual entry" button ("w")
########################################################################################################################


$ACTION
    Case ACTION
        When "FILGAUCHE"   : Gosub FILGAUCHE
        When "AVANT_OUVRE" : Gosub AVANT_OUVRE # 2017-09-21 DNE X3-55850
        When "OUVRE"       : Gosub OUVRE
        When "LIENS"       : Gosub LIENS
        When "STYLE"       : Gosub STYLE
        When "VERIF_MOD"   : Gosub VERIF_MOD
        When "MODIF"       : Gosub MODIF
        When "APRES_MOD"   :  Gosub APRES_MOD
        When "EXEBOUT"     : Gosub EXEBOUT
        When "TRT_DIV"     : Gosub TRT_DIV
        When "STATUT"      : Gosub STATUT
        When "SETBOUT"     : Gosub SETBOUT
        When "FERME"       : Gosub FERME
        When "AFFMASK"     : Gosub AFFMASK
        When "AVANT_SUITE" : Gosub AVANT_SUITE From BSIPAYSEL
        When "APRES_MODIF" : Gosub APRES_MODIF
        When "FIN_ACTION"  : Gosub FIN_ACTION
        When "AVANT_CHOI"  : Gosub AVANT_CHOI
        When Default
    Endcase
Return

########################################################################################################################

$FILGAUCHE
    FILGAUSUP(0) = "[F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD='" + STMCOD + "'"
Return

# 2017-09-21 DNE X3-55850
$AVANT_OUVRE
    If !clalev( [F:BSIIMP] ) : Local File BSIIMP [BSIIMP]   : Endif
    If !clalev( [F:BSIIP] )  : Local File BSIIMPPAR [BSIIP] : Endif

    # Read header record
    Read [F:BSIIMP]BSIIMP0 = SAVCLE2
    If fstat
        GMESSAGE = SAVCLE2 - "~" - mess(1,7703,1) # 'Statement does not exist'
        OK = 0
        Return
    Endif

# X3-208761 2020-07-31 Bader begin
    # Read first transaction record
    Read [F:BSIIMPD]BSIIMPD0 = SAVCLE2;1
    If fstat
        GMESSAGE = SAVCLE2 - "~" - mess(322,7703,1) # 'Statement does not have any transactions.'
        OK = 0
        Return
    Endif
# X3-208761 2020-07-31 Bader begin

    # Read corresponding import settings
    Read [F:BSIIP]BSIIP0 = [F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR
    If fstat
        GMESSAGE = [F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR - "~" - mess(6,7703,1) # 'Import settings not found'
        OK = 0
        Return
    Endif

    # Check if flow type is 'Reconciliation only'. Alert and cancel in case it is.
    If [F:BSIIP]FLOTYP = 2
        GMESSAGE = func AFNC.MES1( mess(241,7703,1), mess(max(1, [F:BSIIP]FLOTYP ),3694,1) ) # "Action not possible for bank statements with flow type '$1$'"
        OK = 0
        Return
    Endif
Return

$OUVRE
    If clalev([F:BSIPAY]) = 0 Then : Local File BSIPAY [BSIPAY]   : Endif  # X3-103296 2018-11-13 Bader
    If clalev([F:BSIMAN]) = 0 Then : Local File BSIMANENT [BSIMAN] : Endif # X3-119483 2019-01-18 Bader
    If clalev([F:BSIDUD]) = 0 Then : Local File BSIDUD [BSIDUD]   : Endif
    If clalev([F:BSIIP])  = 0 Then : Local File BSIIMPPAR [BSIIP] : Endif
    If clalev([F:CPY]) = 0 Then    : Local File COMPANY [CPY]     : Endif
    If clalev([F:TPY]) = 0 Then    : Local File TABPAYTYP [TPY]   : Endif
    If clalev([F:TCU]) = 0 Then    : Local File TABCUR [TCU]      : Endif
    If clalev([F:GTE]) = 0 Then    : Local File GTYPACCENT [GTE]  : Endif
    If clalev([F:SIH]) = 0 Then    : Local File SINVOICE [SIH]    : Endif
    If clalev([F:PIH]) = 0 Then    : Local File PINVOICE [PIH]    : Endif
    If GACTX.AFOLD.AMODULE(5) = [V]CST_AYES # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 BEGIN
        If clalev([F:SOH]) = 0 Then  : Local File SORDER [SOH]    : Endif
    Endif
    If GACTX.AFOLD.AMODULE(6) = [V]CST_AYES
        If clalev([F:POH]) = 0 Then  : Local File PORDER [POH]    : Endif
    Endif # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 END
    If clalev([F:HAE]) = 0 Then    : Local File GACCENTRY [HAE]   : Endif
    If clalev([F:DAE]) = 0 Then    : Local File GACCENTRYD [DAE]  : Endif
    If clalev([F:FIY]) = 0 Then    : Local File FISCALYEAR [FIY]  : Endif
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110
    If clalev([F:PYH]) = 0 Then    : Local File PAYMENTH [PYH]    : Endif
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110 end
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375
    If clalev([F:PYD]) = 0 Then    : Local File PAYMENTD [PYD]    : Endif
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375 End
    If clalev([F:DUD]) = 0 Then    : Local File GACCDUDATE [DUD]  : Endif  # X3-157415 2019-09-04 Bader
    If clalev([F:RBK]) = 0 Then    : Local File RELBANK [RBK]     : Endif  # X3-166805 2019-11-27 Bader

    Global Integer DOMTCLOG : DOMTCLOG = 0     # Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-1501

    Local Char    VALC1(20), VALC2(20), VALC3(20)
Return

$AFFMASK
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(198,7703,1), "1" ) For ACCREF1
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(198,7703,1), "2" ) For ACCREF2
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(198,7703,1), "3" ) For ACCREF3

    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(199,7703,1), "1" ) For BPRREF1
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(199,7703,1), "2" ) For BPRREF2
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(199,7703,1), "3" ) For BPRREF3
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(199,7703,1), "4" ) For BPRREF4
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(199,7703,1), "5" ) For BPRREF5

    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "1" ) For RMTREF1
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "2" ) For RMTREF2
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "3" ) For RMTREF3
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "4" ) For RMTREF4
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "5" ) For RMTREF5
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "6" ) For RMTREF6
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "7" ) For RMTREF7
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "8" ) For RMTREF8
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "9" ) For RMTREF9
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(200,7703,1), "10" ) For RMTREF10

    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(201,7703,1), "1" ) For BANTRSREF1
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(201,7703,1), "2" ) For BANTRSREF2
    Titcol [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG func AFNC.MES1( mess(201,7703,1), "3" ) For BANTRSREF3
Return

$FERME
    Call BSI_UPDATE_STATEMENT_STATE( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD ) From BSILIBMTC
    Kill DOMTCLOG
Return


$LIENS
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110
    Raz [M:BSIMTC00] # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00] = [F:BSIIMPD]
    Raz [M:BSIMTC0]
    Raz [M:BSIMTC4]
    [M:BSIMTC0] = [F:BSIIMPD]
    [M:BSIMTC4] = [F:BSIIMPD]
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110 end
    If [F:BSIIMP]STMCOD <> [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD Then
        Read [F:BSIIMP]BSIIMP0 = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD
    Endif
    Gosub INISTD From BSIMANENT

# Bader: 2016.10-28 X3-6247
#angre X3-133594
#    Case [F:BSIIMPD]SNS
#       When "C" : [M:BSIMTC0]BSISNS = mess(2,3680,1)     # Revenue
#       When "D" : [M:BSIMTC0]BSISNS = mess(1,3680,1)     # Expense
#       When "RC": [M:BSIMTC0]BSISNS = mess(4,3680,1)     # Revenue reversal
#       When "RD": [M:BSIMTC0]BSISNS = mess(3,3680,1)     # Expense reversal
#    Endcase
  [M:BSIMTC0]BSISNS = func GET_SIGN_MESS([F:BSIIMPD]SNS)
# angre X3-133594 end
# Bader: 2016.10-28 X3-6247 end
    [M:BSIMTC00]BLCSTR    = [F:BSIIMP]BLCSTR     # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00]BLCEND    = [F:BSIIMP]BLCEND     # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00]DATSTR    = [F:BSIIMP]DATSTR     # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00]DATEND    = [F:BSIIMP]DATEND     # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00]ORIGNTR   = [F:BSIIMP]ORIGNTR    # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    # TODO(R) X3-56702
    [M:BSIMTC00]BLCSTRSNS = [F:BSIIMP]BLCSTRSNS  # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717
    [M:BSIMTC00]BLCENDSNS = [F:BSIIMP]BLCENDSNS  # 2018-06-27 DNE X3-96717

# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375
    Gosub BUILD_PAYMENT_ARRAY
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375 End
    Local Integer I, J : [L]I = 0
    Gosub READ_BSIDUD                            # X3-103296 2018-11-13 Bader moved to READ_BSIDUD
    Gosub READ_BSIPAY                            # X3-103296 2018-11-13 Bader new
    [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader begin if transaction sign differs from manual entry sign > allow negative TOTMANENT
#    If [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT > 0
    If [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT <> 0
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader end
      [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT -= [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT
    Endif

    # set/reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY
    [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = func GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRPAY()
    If func IS_SAME_BPRPAY([M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY) = [V]CST_AFALSE Then
        [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = ""
    Endif
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY

    # set/reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV
    [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = func GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRINV()
    If func IS_SAME_BPRINV([M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV) = [V]CST_AFALSE Then
        [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = ""
    Endif
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV

    #angre
    If [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY > 0
      [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT -= [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    Endif

    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMTCUR = [M:BSIMTC00]CUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEPCUR = [M:BSIMTC00]CUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMTCUR = [M:BSIMTC00]CUR
    #angre 190916 Including overpayment
    [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAYCUR = [M:BSIMTC00]CUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANCUR = [M:BSIMTC00]CUR

    Gosub UPDATE_NUM

   #    #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-11 - START
    Local Integer C : C = 1
    #Payment reference

    If [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF(0) <> ""
        [M:BSIMTC1]SUMFREREF(C-1) = [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF(0)
        C+=1
     Endif
#
    For [L]I = 1 To dim([F:BSIIMPD]FREREF) - 1
      If [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF([L]I) <> ""
        [M:BSIMTC1]SUMFREREF(C-1) =  [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF([L]I)
         C+=1
      Endif

    Next [L]I
#
#    [M:BSIMTC1]SUMREF += chr$(10)
#
#
    #BP reference
    Local Integer C1 : C1 = 1
    If [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF(0) <> ""
        [M:BSIMTC1]SUMBPRREF(C1-1) =  [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF(0)
        C1+=1
    Endif
#
    For [L]I = 1 To dim([F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF) - 1
        If [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF([L]I) <> ""
            [M:BSIMTC1]SUMBPRREF(C1-1) =  [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF([L]I)
            C1+=1
        Endif
    Next [L]I

    If C > C1
      [M:BSIMTC1]NBLIG = C-1
    Else
      [M:BSIMTC1]NBLIG = C1-1
    Endif
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC1]

#
#    [M:BSIMTC1]SUMREF += chr$(10)
#
#    #Other info
#      [M:BSIMTC1]SUMREF += chr$(10) + mess(263,7703,1)
#      [M:BSIMTC1]SUMREF += chr$(10) + [F:BSIIMPD]REM
#    [M:BSIMTC1]SUMFREREF = [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF(0)
#    For [L]I = 1 To dim([F:BSIIMPD]FREREF) - 1
#        [M:BSIMTC1]SUMFREREF += chr$(10) + [F:BSIIMPD]FREREF([L]I)
#    Next [L]I
#    [M:BSIMTC1]SUMBPRREF = [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF(0)
#    For [L]I = 1 To dim([F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF) - 1
#        [M:BSIMTC1]SUMBPRREF += chr$(10) + [F:BSIIMPD]BPRREF([L]I)
#    Next [L]I
    #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-11 - END

    If [F:BSIIP]CODIMPPAR <> [F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR Then
        Read [F:BSIIP]BSIIP0 = [F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR
    Endif

# Bader: 2017-05-05 X3-35704 show field "Payment no. generated" if B or C match
# angre: 2017-08-09 X3-47569 Add BC match
    If find([F:BSIIMPD]LET,"B","BC","C") and IND > 0 Then  # B or C match and payment found
        [M:BSIMTC0]NUMREG = PYHARR(0)
        [M:BSIMTC0]PAYREF = PYHARR(0)     # Hidden dummy field to avoid the change of shown referenced payment after drill-down
        Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC0]NUMREG With "K:20X"
    Else
        Raz [M:BSIMTC0]NUMREG
        Raz [M:BSIMTC0]PAYREF
        Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC0]NUMREG With "-K:20X"
    Endif
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-35704 End
    #SMO X3-109897
    If [F:BSIIMP]FILFMT <> "BAI2" Then
      Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC00]ORIGNTR With "-K:20X"
    Else
      Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC00]ORIGNTR With "K:20X"
    Endif
    #END SMO X3-109897

    # Update matching information (on tab 2):
    [M:BSIMTC2] = [F:BSIIP]   # Show criteria flags according to configuration
    [M:BSIMTC2] = [F:BSIIMPD] # Show flags according to current matching
    [M:BSIMTC2]PAYREF = [F:BSIIP]PAYREF # PAYREF criterion (same name but different meaning in BSIIP and BSIIMPD)
# X3-188597 2020-04-09 Angre
    [M:BSIMTC2]BPRNAM = [F:BSIIP]BPRNAM # BPRNAM criterion (same name but different meaning in BSIIP and BSIIMPD)
# X3-150002 2019-07-31 Bader begin show fields MTCDATSTR and MTCDATEND
    [M:BSIMTC2]MTCDATSTR = [F:BSIIMP]MTCDATSTR    # start date of matching date range
    [M:BSIMTC2]MTCDATEND = [F:BSIIMP]MTCDATEND    # end date of matching date range
# X3-150002 2019-07-31 Bader end

    # 2017-04-03 ANGRE: X3-30338: Presentation of subdetail information
    Gosub READ_BSIIMPS                            # X3-103296 2018-11-13 Bader moved to READ_BSIIMPS

    #angre 02052017 US X3-33376
    Gosub SET_BP_OVERPAYMENT

# X3-166805 2019-11-27 Bader begin show/hide field "Reconciled"
    # flow type = "Post validation transfer" and transaction not in status "Not validated" > show field "Reconciled"
    If [F:BSIIP]FLOTYP = 3 and [F:BSIIMPD]FLGCRE > 1
      Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC0]FLGRCL With "LA1:1X"
      Local Integer RCL : [L]RCL = [V]CST_AYES
      Filter [F:RBK] Where BSISTM = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD and BSILIN = [F:BSIIMPD]LIN
      For [F:RBK]
          If [F:RBK]CHK = ""    # if at least one RBK transaction has no reconciliation mark > show "not reconciled"
              [L]RCL = [V]CST_ANO
              Break
          Endif
      Next
      [M:BSIMTC0]FLGRCL = [L]RCL
    Else  # flow type <> "Post validation transfer" or transaction in status "Not validated" > don't show field "Reconciled"
      Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC0]FLGRCL With "-LA1:1X"
    Endif
# X3-166805 2019-11-27 Bader end

# X3-215229 2020-09-21 Bader begin make sure the correct grid (OIs or payments) is open for edit depending on matching status
Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1                       # enable open items grid
Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG                        # enable payments grid
Gosub AVANT_CHOI                              # decide whether to disable one of the grids
# X3-215229 2020-09-21 Bader end

    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]
Return

#angre X3-133594
Funprog GET_SIGN_MESS(PSNS)
Value Char PSNS
Local Char SNSMESS(20)
Case PSNS
       When "C" : SNSMESS = mess(2,3680,1)     # Revenue
       When "D" : SNSMESS = mess(1,3680,1)     # Expense
       When "RC": SNSMESS = mess(4,3680,1)     # Revenue reversal
       When "RD": SNSMESS = mess(3,3680,1)     # Expense reversal
    Endcase
End SNSMESS


$SHOW_HIDE_TOTALS
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader begin
Call LECTURE("TCU", [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, "") From CONTOBJ     # Read currency table
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader end
Case [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC
  When "", "M"               # not yet matched or B or C match or manual entry
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMTCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEPCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMTCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAYCUR With "-K:3X"
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader begin
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "-N:13.2"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader end
  When "O"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMTCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEPCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMTCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAYCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANCUR With "-K:3X"
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader begin
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "-N:13.2"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader end
  When "P","PM"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMTCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEPCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMTCUR With "K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAYCUR With "-K:3X"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANCUR With "K:3X"
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader begin
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "-N:13.2"
#   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "N:13.2"
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT With "N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP With "-N3zF:"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT With "N:3zF"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY With "-N:3zF"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
   Chgfmt [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT With "N:3zF"+[F:TCU]CURFMT1
# X3-156158 2019-08-14 Bader end
Endcase
Return



$READ_BSIDUD

#JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - START
Link [F:BSIDUD] With [DUD]DUD8 = NUMDUD As [LNK] Where [F:BSIDUD]STMCOD = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD and [F:BSIDUD]LIN = [F:BSIIMPD]LIN Order By Key LNK0=[F:BSIDUD]STMCOD;[F:BSIDUD]LIN;[F:BSIDUD]LIN1
#Filter [F:BSIDUD] Where [F:BSIDUD]STMCOD = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD and [F:BSIDUD]LIN = [F:BSIIMPD]LIN

#For [F:BSIDUD]BSIDUD0
For [F:LNK]
#JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - END
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375
    [L]J = find([F:BSIDUD]NUM,NUMARR)     # payment found for open item?
    If [L]J > 0
        [M:BSIMTC4]PYHNUM([L]I)   = PYHARR([L]J-1)
    Endif
# Bader: 2017-04-28 X3-33375 End
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDLIN1([L]I)   = [F:BSIDUD]LIN1
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]DUDSEL
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]TYP
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]NUM
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRPAY([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BPRPAY
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BPR
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]AMTCUR
    #JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - START
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) = [F:DUD]AMTCUR-[F:DUD]TMPCUR-[F:DUD]PAYCUR #Currency
    #JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - END
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]CUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOC([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]AMTLOC
    #JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - START
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) = [F:DUD]AMTLOC-[F:DUD]TMPLOC-[F:DUD]PAYLOC #Amount in currency
    #JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - END
    Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I) = [F:CPY]ACCCUR
# Bader: 2016.10-28 X3-6243
    If [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = 0     # temporary until migration will be available
       If [F:BSIIMPD]SNS = "C" or [F:BSIIMPD]SNS = "RD" : [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = [F:BSIDUD]SNS : Endif
       If [F:BSIIMPD]SNS = "D" or [F:BSIIMPD]SNS = "RC" : [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = -[F:BSIDUD]SNS : Endif
    Endif
# Bader: 2016.10-28 X3-6243 end
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYCUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPCUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYLOC
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPLOC
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYSTM
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPSTM
    [M:BSIMTC4]BPRVCR([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]BPRVCR
    [M:BSIMTC4]DEPAMT([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]DEPAMT
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDDAT([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]DUDDAT
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]FCY
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSAC([L]I)    = [F:BSIDUD]SAC
    Read [F:DAE]DAE2 = [F:BSIDUD]ACCNUM
    If fstat = 0 Then
        [M:BSIMTC4]DAEACC([L]I) = [F:DAE]ACC
    Endif
    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        #X3-42425 If different currencys use statement currency
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
        Else
          [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
        Endif
    Endif
    [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 += 1
    [S]nolign += 1
    [L]I += 1
Next
Filter [F:BSIDUD]   # SAM 120988 Bader 2017-01-19
#JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - START
Filter [F:DUD]
#JOJAC - X3-186063 - 2020-05-08 - END

Return


$READ_BSIIMPS
Raz [M:BSIMTC3]
If clalev([F:IIMPS]) = 0 Then : Local File BSIIMPDS [IIMPS]   : Endif
Filter  [F:IIMPS] Where [F:IIMPS]STMCOD = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD and [F:IIMPS]TRSLIN = [F:BSIIMPD]LIN
If rowcount([F:IIMPS]) > 0
   For [F:IIMPS]BSIIMPS0
    [M:BSIMTC3]AMTCURS([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]AMTCURS
    [M:BSIMTC3]CURS([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)         = [F:IIMPS]CURS
    [M:BSIMTC3]SNSS([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)         = [F:IIMPS]SNSS
    [M:BSIMTC3]ACCREF1([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]ACCREF(0)
    [M:BSIMTC3]ACCREF2([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]ACCREF(1)
    [M:BSIMTC3]ACCREF3([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]ACCREF(2)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BPRREF1([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]BPRREFS(0)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BPRREF2([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]BPRREFS(1)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BPRREF3([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]BPRREFS(2)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BPRREF4([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]BPRREFS(3)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BPRREF5([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]BPRREFS(4)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF1([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(0)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF2([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(1)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF3([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(2)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF4([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(3)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF5([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(4)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF6([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(5)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF7([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(6)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF8([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(7)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF9([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(8)
    [M:BSIMTC3]RMTREF10([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)     = [F:IIMPS]RMTREF(9)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BANTRSREF1([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)   = [F:IIMPS]BANTRSREF(0)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BANTRSREF2([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)   = [F:IIMPS]BANTRSREF(1)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BANTRSREF3([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)   = [F:IIMPS]BANTRSREF(2)
    [M:BSIMTC3]BVRREF([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)       = [F:IIMPS]BVRREF
    [M:BSIMTC3]PAYREFS([M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG)      = [F:IIMPS]PAYREFS
    [M:BSIMTC3]NBLIG += 1
  Next
Endif
Filter [F:IIMPS]
Affzo [M:BSIMTC3]
Return


$READ_BSIPAY
Raz [L]I
Filter [F:BSIPAY] Where [F:BSIPAY]STMCOD = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD and [F:BSIPAY]LIN = [F:BSIIMPD]LIN
For [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAY0
    [M:BSIMTC4]LIN1([L]I)      = [F:BSIPAY]LIN1
    [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]I)    = [F:BSIPAY]PAYSEL
    [M:BSIMTC4]NUM([L]I)       = [F:BSIPAY]NUM
    [M:BSIMTC4]ISPAY([L]I)     = [F:BSIPAY]ISPAY
    [M:BSIMTC4]CURP([L]I)      = [F:BSIPAY]CUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]BPR([L]I)       = [F:BSIPAY]BPR
    [M:BSIMTC4]SNSP([L]I)      = [F:BSIPAY]SNS
    [M:BSIMTC4]AMTCURP([L]I)   = [F:BSIPAY]AMTCUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]BANPAYTPY([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BANPAYTPY
    [M:BSIMTC4]TYP([L]I)       = [F:BSIPAY]TYP
    [M:BSIMTC4]BANP([L]I)      = [F:BSIPAY]BAN
# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader begin to make sure BSISNS has a value other than 0
    If [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS = 0 : [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS = 1 : Endif
#    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYCUR
#    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYSTM
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS * [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYCUR
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS * [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYSTM
# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader end
    If [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I)
    Endif
    [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG += 1
    [S]nolign += 1
    [L]I += 1
Next
Filter [F:BSIPAY]
If [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "PM"       # payment match with manual entry > calculate TOTMANENT
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader begin if transaction sign differs from manual entry sign > multiply amount by -1
    Local Integer TRS_SNS
    If ([F:BSIIMPD]SNS="C" | [F:BSIIMPD]SNS="RD") : TRS_SNS = 2 : Endif
    If ([F:BSIIMPD]SNS="D" | [F:BSIIMPD]SNS="RC") : TRS_SNS = 1 : Endif
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader end
    Filter [F:BSIMAN] Where STMCOD = [M:BSIMTC0]STMCOD and LIN = [M:BSIMTC0]LIN
    For [F:BSIMAN]
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader begin if transaction sign differs from manual entry sign > multiply amount by -1
      If [L]TRS_SNS <> [F:BSIMAN]SNS
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT += ([F:BSIMAN]AMT * -1)
      Else
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader end
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTMANENT += [F:BSIMAN]AMT
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader begin if transaction sign differs from manual entry sign > multiply amount by -1
      Endif
# X3-211540 2020-09-22 Bader end
    Next
    Filter [F:BSIMAN]
Endif
Return



 #angre 02052017 US X3-33376
 #Deactivate Overpayment if open items from different BPs are selected
$SET_BP_OVERPAYMENT
    Local Integer J
    Local Char LBPR(GLONBPR)
    Local Tinyint FLGMULTIBP
    LBPR = ""
    For [L]J = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
      If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]J) = [V]CST_AYES
        If LBPR <> "" and LBPR <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]J)
          [L]FLGMULTIBP = [V]CST_AYES
          Raz[M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
          Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
          Break
        Else
          LBPR = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]J)
        Endif
      Endif
    Next [L]J
    If [L]FLGMULTIBP <> [V]CST_AYES
      Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    Endif
Return

$BUILD_PAYMENT_ARRAY
Link [F:PYH] With [F:PYD]PYD0(1)=[F:PYH]NUM As [LPYH]
&            Where [F:PYH]BSITRS = [F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD + "/" + num$([F:BSIIMPD]LIN)
&            Order By Key LPYH = [F:PYD]BPRLIN Asc

Local Integer MYCNT : MYCNT = rowcount([LPYH]) + 1
Local Char NUMARR(GLONVCR) (MYCNT)   # array of invoice numbers
Local Char PYHARR(GLONVCR) (MYCNT)   # array of payment numbers
Local Integer IND : IND = 0
Raz NUMARR, PYHARR

For [LPYH]
# X3-119483 2019-01-17 Bader begin > handle manual entries for payment matching
#    If find([F:BSIIMPD]LET,"A","AM","AC") Then   # A or AM match (with open items matched) # angre: 2017-08-09 X3-47569 Add AC match
    If find([F:BSIIMPD]LET,"A","AM","AC") and left$([F:BSIIMPD]TYPMTC,1) <> "P" Then   # A/AC or AM match (with open items matched) and no payment matched
# X3-119483 2019-01-17 Bader end
        If !find([F:PYD]VCRNUM,NUMARR)      # not yet in array
            NUMARR(IND) = [F:PYD]VCRNUM     # remember invoice number
            PYHARR(IND) = [F:PYD]NUM        # remember payment number
            IND += 1
        Endif
    Else                                    # AD, AS, B or C match or AM payment match
        PYHARR(IND) = [F:PYD]NUM            # for AD, AS, B and C matches only the payment number is relevant
        IND += 1
    Endif
Next
Return


$STYLE
    #TODO(R): Implement control for "No manual entry for transaction"
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM
    Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM
    If [F:BSIIMP]FLGMTC = 3 Then
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL
    Else
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL
    Endif

    # DNE X3-53026
    Local Integer I
    For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        Gosub ACTZO_DISZO_GRID_LINE
    Next
Return

$VERIF_MOD
# X3-119483 2019-01-15 Bader begin
#    If [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT <> 0 Then
Local Integer I, PAYMATCH
Local Decimal AMTALLOC, AMTMAN
Raz PAYMATCH, AMTALLOC, AMTMAN
    If [M:BSIMTC0]LET = "AP" or ([M:BSIMTC0]LET = "AM") and find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG-1)) > 0
        If [M:BSIMTC0]LET = "AM"              # check if total of picked payments + manual entry = transaction amount
            For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG - 1
                If [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES : AMTALLOC += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I) : Endif
            Next [L]I
            Filter [F:BSIMAN] Where STMCOD = [M:BSIMTC0]STMCOD and LIN = [M:BSIMTC0]LIN
            For [F:BSIMAN]
                AMTMAN += [F:BSIMAN]AMT
            Next
            Filter [F:BSIMAN]
#            Infbox "allocated: " + num$(AMTALLOC) + ", manually: " + num$(AMTMAN) + ", total: " + num$(AMTALLOC+AMTMAN)
            If AMTALLOC + AMTMAN = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR
                PAYMATCH = 1           # "AP" or "AM" and at least one payment ticked manually > everything OK
            Endif
        Endif
    Endif
    If [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT <> 0 and PAYMATCH = 0 Then
# X3-119483 2019-01-15 Bader end
        Errbox(mess(37,7703,1)) # 'The transaction amount is not completely allocated.'
        OK = 0
    Else
        # Prevent class object from complaining about different update ticks.
        If dim( ANOUPDTICK ) > 0
            ANOUPDTICK = 1
        Endif
    Endif
Return

$MODIF
    # Switch back to update tick check in class object handling.
    If dim( ANOUPDTICK ) > 0
        ANOUPDTICK = 0
    Endif
Return

$APRES_MOD
    Local Integer I, STA
# X3-157415 2019-09-04 Bader begin
    Local Decimal DIFF
# X3-157415 2019-09-04 Bader end
    Raz fstat
    Trbegin [F:BSIDUD],[F:BSIPAY]
    For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        Read [F:BSIDUD]BSIDUD0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN;[M:BSIMTC4]DUDLIN1([L]I)
        If fstat = 0 Then
            [F:BSIDUD]DUDSEL    = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I)
# X3-157415 2019-09-04 Bader begin update [F:DUD]TMPCUR and [F:DUD]TMPLOC if something has changed
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update [F:DUD] also if OI not selected (might have been de-selected)
#            If [F:BSIDUD]DUDSEL = [V]CST_AYES and [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYCUR <> abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I))
            If [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYCUR <> abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)) or [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPCUR <> abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I))
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
                DIFF = ([F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYCUR+[F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPCUR) - (abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I))+abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)))
                If DIFF <> 0                              # something has changed
                    Read [F:DUD]DUD8=[F:BSIDUD]NUMDUD     # read corresponding record in GACCDUDATE to update it
                    If !fstat                             # found
                        [F:DUD]TMPCUR -= DIFF             # update temporariliy paid amount in open item

                        # check if company currency <> transaction currency, if yes calculate DIFF in transaction currency
                        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
                            Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
                            Call LEC_TPY_LEG([F:BSIIP]LEG, [F:BSIIP]PAYTYP) From CPTLEC # read payment entry type
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin calculate DIFF from statement currency
#                            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, DIFF, DIFF, [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
                            DIFF = ([F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYSTM+[F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPSTM) - (abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I))+abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)))
                            [F:DUD]TMPLOC -= DIFF             # update temporariliy paid amount in open item
#                            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP,
#&                            [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I))+abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)),
#&                            [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
                            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I), [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP,
&                            [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [F:DUD]TMPLOC, [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
                            # we write converted BSIPAYSTM+BSIDEPSTM in BSIPAYLOC to indicate that company currency <> transaction currency
#                        Else
#                            DIFF = ([F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYSTM+[F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPSTM) - (abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I))+abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)))
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
# X3-224026 2020-11-16 Bader begin update [F:DUD]TMPLOC also when transaction currency = OI currency (regression X3-200184)
                        Else                              # open item currency = transaction currency
                            [F:DUD]TMPLOC -= DIFF         # update temporariliy paid amount in open item
# X3-224026 2020-11-16 Bader end
                        Endif
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin calculate DIFF from statement currency
#                        [F:DUD]TMPLOC -= DIFF             # update temporariliy paid amount in open item
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin end
                        If [F:DUD]TMPCUR = [F:DUD]AMTCUR  # totally assigned
                            [F:DUD]FLGCLE = 4
                        Else                              # partially or not assigned
                            [F:DUD]FLGCLE = 1
                        Endif
                        Rewrite [F:DUD]
                        If fstat Break Endif
                    Endif
                Endif
            Endif
# X3-157415 2019-09-04 Bader end
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYCUR = abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I))
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPCUR = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I))
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYLOC = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I))
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPLOC = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I))
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIPAYSTM = abs([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I))
            [F:BSIDUD]BSIDEPSTM = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I))
            Rewrite [F:BSIDUD]
            If fstat <> 0 Then
#                Errbox("Failed to update:" - [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD - "~" - num$([M:BSIMTC0]LIN) - "~" - num$([M:BSIMTC0]LIN1([L]I)))
                Break
            Endif
        Endif
    Next [L]I
# X3-119483 2019-01-18 Bader begin
    # update table BSIPAY
    If fstat = 0 Then
        For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG - 1
            Read [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAY0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN;[M:BSIMTC4]LIN1([L]I)
            If fstat = 0 Then
                [F:BSIPAY]PAYSEL    = [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]I)
                [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYCUR = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I))
                [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAYSTM = abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I))
                Rewrite [F:BSIPAY]
                If fstat <> 0 Then
                    Break
                Endif
            Endif
        Next [L]I
    Endif
# X3-119483 2019-01-18 Bader end
    If fstat = 0 Then
        Commit
    Else
        Rollback
    Endif

    # Refresh left list
    ILIS = val( right$( currbox, 8 ) )
    Gosub REMP_LISGAU From GOBJSUB
Return

$EXEBOUT
    Case BOUT
        When "m", "r", "v", "w", "s", "p" # Note: Button "v" is only for testing purposes and is not develivered to the customer.
# 2018-07-02 DNE X3-96717
#        When "m", "r", "v", "w" # Note: Button "v" is only for testing purposes and is not develivered to the customer.
            # Refresh left list
            ILIS = val( right$( currbox, 8 ) )
            Gosub REMP_LISGAU From GOBJSUB
        When "B"                # after drill-down to payment reset dummy payment reference field
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110
            [M:BSIMTC0]PAYREF = [M:BSIMTC0]NUMREG   # fill hidden dummy field for drill down
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110 end
    Endcase
Return

$TRT_DIV
    Case TRAIT
        When "CONSBSI" :
            Local Integer FIY : Raz FIY
            Local Integer ASTATUS : [L]ASTATUS = [V]CST_AOK
            Local Char ERRMES(255) : Raz ERRMES

            ASTATUS = func FINPER_SYRA.GET_FIY( GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CPY, GTYPGEN, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, FIY, ERRMES )
    Endcase
Return

$STATUT
    Case BOUT
        When "w"
# 2018-07-02 DNE X3-96717
#        When "s", "p", "w"
            # Refresh left list
            ILIS = val( right$( currbox, 8 ) )
            Gosub REMP_LISGAU From GOBJSUB
    Endcase
Return

$SETBOUT
# X3-120227 2018-12-12 Bader begin
#    Call VIREBOUT( CHAINE, "rmvwac" ) From GOBJET
    Call VIREBOUT( CHAINE, "rmvwabc" ) From GOBJET
# X3-120227 2018-12-12 Bader begin
    If VERROU and ( [M:BSIMTC0]FLGCRE = 1)              # matching and undo of matching for non validated transactions
        If [M:BSIMTC0]LET = ""
            CHAINE += "m"                               # match transaction
        Else
            CHAINE += "rv"                              # undo matching
        Endif
    Endif
    If [M:BSIMTC0]LET <> "" and !find([M:BSIMTC0]FLGCRE,2,4) # if already matched but neither completely validated nor manually closed
        CHAINE += "c"                                   # close transaction
    Endif
    If [M:BSIMTC0]LET <> "" and (find([M:BSIMTC0]LET,"AD","AS","AM") or left$([M:BSIMTC0]LET, 1) <> "A") Then
# X3-225351 2020-11-30 Bader begin when transaction is in status "manually completed" or "validated" > no manual entry for B/C
#        If [M:BSIMTC0]LET <> "AM" or find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG-1)) > 0       # not "AM" or at least one payment ticked manually
        # manual entry active if:
        # - AD, AS where manual entry already exists (must be visible independent from the transaction status)
        # - B, BC, BP, C until transaction is validated or manually completed
        # - AM + type PM where manual entry already exists as additon to payment matching (must be visible independent from the transaction status)
        # - AM + not yet validated or manually completed and a payment has been ticked manually (type is still empty or P, first entering of manual entry for payment matching)
        If find([M:BSIMTC0]LET,"AD","AS") or
&          (left$([M:BSIMTC0]LET, 1) <> "A" and !find([M:BSIMTC0]FLGCRE,2,4)) or
&          ([M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "PM") or
&          ([M:BSIMTC0]FLGCRE = 1 and find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG-1)) > 0)
# X3-225351 2020-11-30 Bader end
            CHAINE += "w"                                   # manual entry
        Endif
        If [M:BSIMTC0]FLGCRE = 1                        # if not yet validated or partially validated or manually closed
          If !find([M:BSIMTC0]LET,"AD","AS")
              CHAINE += "ab"                            # manual selection/payment selection
          Endif
        Endif
    Endif
# 2018-07-02 DNE X3-96717
    Call VIREBOUT( CHMEN, "spl" ) From GOBJET            # match / validate statement / Activate log
    CHMEN += "sp"                                        # match / validate statement
    If DOMTCLOG = 0
        CHMEN += "l"                                     # activate log
    Endif
    Call VIREBOUT( CHMEN, "1" ) From GOBJET            # Zoom Payment
    Gosub BUILD_PAYMENT_ARRAY
    If IND > 0                                         # activate "Payment" link if payment found
        CHMEN += "1"
    Endif
Return

############################################################################################
Subprog BSIMTCTRS()
    If !clalev ([F:BSIIMPD]) : Local File BSIIMPD [BSIIMPD] Endif # Details import

    Local Clbfile MSG(1)
    Local Integer STA

    # Start database transaction
    Trbegin [F:BSIIMPD], [F:BSIDUD]

    Call BSI_MATCHING([M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,[M:BSIMTC0]LIN,STA,MSG,DOMTCLOG) From BSILIBMTC
    If STA <> 0
        # Rollback transaction and display error message.
        Rollback
        Errbox(MSG)
    Else
        # Commit transaction and update screen.
        Commit
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG = 0
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 = 0
        [M:BSIMTC0] = [F:BSIIMPD]
        Gosub LIENS                      # read open items
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC2]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC3]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]
        If MSG <> "" : Infbox(MSG) Titled mess(66,123,1) : Endif # 'Warning'
    Endif
End


##################################################
Subprog BSIMTCRES()
    If !clalev ([F:BSIIMPD]) : Local File BSIIMPD [BSIIMPD] Endif # Details import

    Local Char MSG(250)
    Local Integer STA

    # Start database transaction
    Trbegin [F:BSIIMPD]

    Call BSI_UNMATCH( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD, [M:BSIMTC0]LIN, STA, MSG ) From BSILIBMTC
    If STA
        # Rollback transaction and display error message.
        Rollback
        Errbox( MSG )
    Else
        # Commit transaction and update screen.
        Commit
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG = 0
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 = 0
        [M:BSIMTC0] = [F:BSIIMPD]
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
        [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Gosub LIENS                      # read open items
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC2]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]
    Endif
End

########################################################################################################################

Subprog BSIMTCSTM()
Local Integer STA
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
If GREP = ""              # Save button inactive
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
    If !clalev ([F:BSIIMP])    Local File BSIIMP      [BSIIMP]  Endif # Header import
    If !clalev ([F:BSIIMPD])   Local File BSIIMPD     [BSIIMPD] Endif # Details import

    Local Clbfile MSG(3)

    # Start database transaction
    Trbegin [F:BSIIMP], [F:BSIIMPD]

    Call BSI_MATCH_STATEMENT( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD, STA, MSG, DOMTCLOG ) From BSILIBMTC
    If STA
        # Rollback transaction and display error message.
        Rollback
        Errbox( MSG )
    Else
        # Commit transaction and update screen.
        Commit
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG = 0
        [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 = 0
        [M:BSIMTC0] = [F:BSIIMPD]
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
        [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Gosub LIENS                      # read open items
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]
        If MSG <> "" : Infbox(MSG) Titled mess(66,123,1) : Endif # 'Warning'
    Endif
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
Else                      # Save button active > no validation before saving the changes
    Infbox mess(558,9900,1) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA # 'Please save the modifications before continuing.'
Endif
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
End

########################################################################################################################

# Note: Button "v" is only for testing purposes and is not develivered to the customer.
Subprog BSIPAYTRS()
Local Char MSG(250)
Local Integer STA

# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
If GREP = ""              # Save button inactive
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
    # Open trace file
    Call OUVRE_TRACE(mess(40,7703,1)) From LECFIC  # Bank statement import: payment creation
    Call ECR_TRACE ("-----------------------------------------------------------------------",0) From GESECRAN

    # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader begin
    # create reconciliation header and footer for statement (transactions created in BSI_PAYMENT_CREATION)
    Call BSI_RCL_CREATE_HEADER_AND_FOOTER([M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,STA,MSG,1) From BSILIBRCL
    If !STA
    # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader end
      Call BSI_PAYMENT_CREATION([M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,[M:BSIMTC0]LIN,STA,MSG) From BSILIBPAY
      If STA <> 0
          Errbox( MSG )
          Call ECR_TRACE(MSG,1) From GESECRAN
          # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader begin
          # delete RELBANK header/footer in case of error if flowtype = "Post validation transfer"
          Call BSI_RCL_DELETE([M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,STA,MSG,1) From BSILIBRCL
          # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader end
      Else
          Call ECR_TRACE(mess(56,7703,1),0) From GESECRAN  # Bank statement import: payment validation
          Call BSI_PAYMENT_VALIDATION([F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR,[M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,STA,MSG) From BSILIBPAY
          If STA <> 0
              Call ECR_TRACE(MSG,1) From GESECRAN
              Errbox( MSG )
          Endif

          # Update screen.
          Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL
          Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL
          [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG = 0
          [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 = 0
          [M:BSIMTC0] = [F:BSIIMPD]
          Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
          Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
          #angre
          Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
          [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
          Gosub LIENS                      # read open items
          Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]
          Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]
          Call BSI_UPDATE_STATEMENT_STATE( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD ) From BSILIBMTC
      Endif
    # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader begin
    Endif
    # X3-166778 2019-11-12 Bader end

    # Close trace file
    Call FERME_TRACE From LECFIC
    Call LEC_TRACE From LECFIC
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
Else                      # Save button active > no validation before saving the changes
    Infbox mess(558,9900,1) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
Endif
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
End

########################################################################################################################

Subprog BSIPAYSTM()
    Local Char MSG(255)
    Local Integer STA : STA = 1

# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
    If GREP = ""              # Save button inactive
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
        # DNE X3-52272
        If [F:BSIIP]FLGCLS = 2
            #  'Generate payments and validate all transactions?'
            #  'Note: Status B and C will be set to completed.'
            Wrnbox mess(58,7703,1), func AFNC.MES1( mess(236,7703,1), [F:BSIIP]ACCSUSPENSE ) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
        Else
          #  'Generate payments and validate all transactions?'
          #  'Note: Status B and C will be posted to suspense account $1$.'
          Wrnbox mess(58,7703,1), func AFNC.MES1( mess(59,7703,1), [F:BSIIP]ACCSUSPENSE ) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
        Endif
        If STA = 1 # STA = 1 means "OK button pressed". So let's proceed.
            # Create payments for a whole statement.
            Call BSI_PAYMENT_CREATION_STATEMENT( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD, STA, MSG ) From BSILIBPAY

            # Validate payments
            Call BSI_PAYMENT_VALIDATION( [F:BSIIMP]CODIMPPAR, [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD, STA, MSG ) From BSILIBPAY
            If STA
                Call ECR_TRACE( MSG, 1 ) From GESECRAN
            Endif
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110
            Read [F:BSIIMPD]BSIIMPD0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN  # read again to update screen
            Call BSI_UPDATE_STATEMENT_STATE( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD ) From BSILIBMTC
            Gosub LIENS                                                  # read data and set screen values
            Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]                                            # refresh screen
            Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]                                            # refresh screen
# Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-4110 end
        Endif
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060
    Else                      # Save button active > no validation before saving the changes
        Infbox mess(558,9900,1) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
    Endif
# Bader: 2017-02-20 X3-26060 end
End

########################################################################################################################
# Close a transaction manually
########################################################################################################################
Subprog BSICLOTRS()
    Local Char MSG(255)
    Local Integer STA : STA = 1

    If GREP = ""              # Save button inactive
        Wrnbox mess(218,7703,1), mess(217,7703,1), mess(1370,9900,1) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
        #  'Closing of the transaction cannot be undone.'
        #  'No payments will be created for closed transactions.'
        #  'Do you want to proceed?'

        If STA = 1 # STA = 1 means "OK button pressed". So let's proceed.
            Call BSI_CLOSE_TRANSACTION([M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD,[M:BSIMTC0]LIN,STA,MSG) From BSILIBPAY
            If STA
                Errbox( MSG )
            Endif
            Read [F:BSIIMPD]BSIIMPD0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN  # read again to update screen
            Call BSI_UPDATE_STATEMENT_STATE( [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD ) From BSILIBMTC
            Gosub LIENS                                                  # read data and set screen values
            Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]                                            # refresh screen
            Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]                                            # refresh screen
        Endif
    Else                      # Save button active > no validation before saving the changes
        Infbox mess(558,9900,1) Titled mess(66,123,1) Using STA
    Endif
End

########################################################################################################################

Subprog IB_NBLIG1
    GBOUT1 = mess(4,413,1)+"/"+mess(2,413,1)
End

########################################################################################################################

Subprog B1_NBLIG1
    Local Integer NOL
    [L]NOL = nolign - 1

    Read [F:BSIDUD]BSIDUD0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN;[M:BSIMTC4]DUDLIN1([L]NOL)
    If fstat <> 0 Then
        End
    Endif

    Local Char PROTYP(GLONGTE), BPCTYP(GLONGTE), BPSTYP(GLONGTE)
    Call PARAM([F:BSIDUD]CPY, "BPCORDTYP", [L]BPCTYP) From ADOVAL : # CCL
    If [L]BPCTYP = "" Then
        [L]BPCTYP = "*SO"
    Endif
    Call PARAM([F:BSIDUD]CPY, "BPSORDTYP", [L]BPSTYP) From ADOVAL : # CCF
    If [L]BPSTYP = "" Then
        [L]BPSTYP = "*PO"
    Endif
    If func AFNC.ACTIV("KIT")   # Issue X3-107197
      Call PARAM([F:BSIDUD]CPY, "BPSPROTYP", [L]PROTYP) From ADOVAL : # PRO
    Endif   # Issue X3-107197
    # Version client / serveur : on ferme et ré-ouvre les fichiers avant et aprčs le tunnel
    Local Char VALC2(20)
    [L]VALC2 = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM([L]NOL)

    Local Integer IPTTYP
    [L]IPTTYP = 0
    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) <> "" Then
        Call LEC_GTE_LEG(GCURLEG, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL)) From CPTLEC
        If fstat Then
            Case [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL)
                When [L]BPCTYP, "*SO" : [L]IPTTYP = 1
                When [L]BPSTYP, "*PO" : [L]IPTTYP = 2
                When [L]PROTYP        : [L]IPTTYP = 4
                When Default          : [L]IPTTYP = 0
            Endcase
        Else
            [L]IPTTYP = 3
        Endif
    Endif
    Gosub AB3_FACCDE
    Call OBJET([L]VALC1, [L]VALC2, [L]VALC3) From GOBJET
End

########################################################################################################################

Subprog C_DUDSEL(VALEUR)
    Variable Integer VALEUR
    Local Integer I

    If VALEUR = [V]CST_AYES Then
        If not [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT > 0 Then
            For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
                If [L]I <> [S]nolign - 1 and [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
                    Errbox(mess(46,191,1) - "0.")
                    mkstat = 2
                    Break
                Endif
            Next [L]I
        Endif
        For [L]I = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
            If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
# TODO (DNE): Restriction to single site can be removed in the future (and of course the whole loop for it will be empty.).
                If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([S]nolign - 1) Then
                    Errbox(mess(57,7703,1) - "'" + [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([L]I) + "'.")
                    mkstat = 2
                    Break
                Endif
            Endif
        Next [L]I

# X3-223301 2020-11-13 Bader begin add check if OI already selected in another transaction
        # check if open item already matched to another transaction and selected
        If clalev([F:BSIDUD1]) = 0 Then : Local File BSIDUD [BSIDUD1]   : Endif
        If clalev([F:DUD1])    = 0 Then : Local File GACCDUDATE [DUD1]   : Endif
        # check if open item already matched to another transaction and selected
        Filter [F:BSIDUD1] Where NUM = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM(nolign-1) and [F:BSIDUD1]DUDSEL = [V]CST_AYES
&              and ([F:BSIDUD1]STMCOD <> [M:BSIMTC0]STMCOD or [F:BSIDUD1]LIN <> [M:BSIMTC0]LIN)
        For [F:BSIDUD1]
          Read [F:DUD1]DUD1 = [F:BSIDUD1]ACCNUM; [F:BSIDUD1]DUDLIG    # read original DUD record to find out if already totally assigned
          If [F:DUD1]AMTCUR - [F:DUD1]PAYCUR - [F:DUD1]TMPCUR = 0     # check if totally assigned > if yes: error
            mkstat = 2
            GMESSAGE = func AFNC.MES2(mess(323,7703,1),[F:BSIDUD1]NUM,[F:BSIDUD1]STMCOD+"/"+num$([F:BSIDUD1]LIN))
            Break
          Endif
        Next
        Filter [F:BSIDUD1]
# X3-223301 2020-11-13 Bader end
    Endif
End


Subprog AM_DUDSEL(VALEUR)
    Variable Integer VALEUR
    Local Integer I, J
    Local Integer LDELAI
    Local Decimal LTAUX_ESC, LMONT_ESC
    Local Integer SELECTED
    Local Char LCURLEG(GLONADI)
    Local Integer STA

    [L]I = [S]nolign - 1
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = VALEUR
    Read [F:BSIDUD]BSIDUD0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN;[M:BSIMTC4]DUDLIN1([L]I)
# X3-224501 2020-12-02 Bader begin recalculate [F:BSIDUD]BALDUD from original open item as OI might be ticked already in another transaction
    [F:BSIDUD]BALDUD = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) # get remaining amount of the OI in transaction currency
# X3-224501 2020-12-02 Bader end

    If [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = 0     # temporary until migration will be available
       If [M:BSIMTC0]SNS = "C" or [M:BSIMTC0]SNS = "RD" : [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = [F:BSIDUD]SNS : Endif
       If [M:BSIMTC0]SNS = "D" or [M:BSIMTC0]SNS = "RC" : [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS = -[F:BSIDUD]SNS : Endif
    Endif

    If VALEUR = [V]CST_AYES Then
        # calculate discount
        [L]LCURLEG = [V]GCURLEG
        [V]GCURLEG = [F:BSIIP]LEG
        Call ESC_AGIO([F:BSIDUD]DEP, [F:BSIDUD]BALDUD, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDDAT([L]I) + [F:BSIIP]DEPTOL,
&           [L]LDELAI, [L]LTAUX_ESC, [L]LMONT_ESC, [F:BSIDUD]ACCNUM, [F:BSIDUD]DUDLIG) From TRTDIV
        [V]GCURLEG = [L]LCURLEG
        If [L]LMONT_ESC <> 0 Then
            Call LECTURE("TCU", [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, "") From CONTOBJ
            [L]LMONT_ESC = arr([L]LMONT_ESC, [F:TCU]CURRND)
        Endif

        If [L]LMONT_ESC > 0 Then
            # late charges are not considered
            [L]LMONT_ESC = 0
        Endif

        # LMONT_ESC and [F:BSIDUD]BALDUD are always in transaction currency (not in OI currency)
        # > therefore assign values to fields for statement (=transaction) currency
        [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * abs([L]LMONT_ESC)
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIDUD]BSISNS * ([F:BSIDUD]BALDUD - abs([M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)))

        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
          Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
          Call LEC_TPY_LEG([F:BSIIP]LEG, [F:BSIIP]PAYTYP) From CPTLEC # read payment entry type
          If [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT < [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) Then      # open item is not totally assigned because OI amount bigger than rest amount
              Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
              Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
              [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
              # convert only if open item not totally assigned, otherwise we can use open item amount in open item currency
              Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I), [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
          Else  # open item is totally assigned, therefore we can use open item amount in open item currency
              Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I), [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
              Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I), [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
          Endif
        Else    # if statement currency = OI currency assign values in statement currency to all amount fields
          If [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT < [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) Then
              Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
              [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
          Endif
          [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
          [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
        Endif


        # update totals
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)

        # update remaining OI amount in screen
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) -= ([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) + [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I))
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) -= ([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) + [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I))

        # following values are controlled in C_DUDSEL
        [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]I)
        [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([L]I)
    Else
        # update totals
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT -= [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP -= [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)

        # update remaining OI amount in screen
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) += ([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) + [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I))
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) += ([M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) + [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I))

        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I)
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I)
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
    Endif
    [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
    [M:BSIMTC0]LET = "AM"

    Gosub COUNT_SELECTED

    If VALEUR = [V]CST_AYES Then
        [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "O"             # set [M:BSIMTC0]MTCTYP
        If func IS_SAME_BPRPAY([M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRPAY([L]I)) = [V]CST_ATRUE Then
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRPAY([L]I)  # set [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY
        Else
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY
        Endif
        If func IS_SAME_BPRINV([M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]I)) Then
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]I)  # set [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV
        Else
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV
        Endif
        [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDFCY([L]I) # set [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN
    Else
        If [L]SELECTED = 0 Then
            [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV
            [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN = ""          # reset [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN
        Else
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = func GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRPAY()
            If func IS_SAME_BPRPAY([M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY) = [V]CST_AFALSE Then
                [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY = ""
            Endif
            [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = func GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRINV()
            If func IS_SAME_BPRINV([M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV) = [V]CST_AFALSE Then
                [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV = ""
            Endif
        Endif
    Endif

    Gosub UPDATE_NUM
    Gosub SET_BP_OVERPAYMENT
    Gosub ACTZO_DISZO_GRID_LINE

    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]BPRINV
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]BPRPAY
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]FCYLIN
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]LET
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC

    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I)
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I)
End

# DNE X3-53026
$ACTZO_DISZO_GRID_LINE
    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I)
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I)
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
    Else
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I)
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I)
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)
    Endif
Return

$COUNT_SELECTED
    [L]SELECTED = 0
    For [L]J = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        If [L]I <> [L]J and [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]J) = [V]CST_AYES Then
            [L]SELECTED = 1
            Break
        Endif
    Next [L]J
Return

Funprog IS_SAME_BPRPAY(VBPRPAY)
    Value Char VBPRPAY()
    Local Integer K
    For [L]K = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]K) = [V]CST_AYES Then
            # only selected lines
            If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRPAY([L]K) <> VBPRPAY Then
                End [V]CST_AFALSE
            Endif
        Endif
    Next [L]K
End [V]CST_ATRUE

Funprog IS_SAME_BPRINV(VBPRINV)
    Value Char VBPRINV()
    Local Integer K
    For [L]K = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]K) = [V]CST_AYES Then
            # only selected lines
            If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]K) <> VBPRINV Then
                End [V]CST_AFALSE
            Endif
        Endif
    Next [L]K
End [V]CST_ATRUE

Funprog GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRPAY()
    Local Integer K
    For [L]K = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]K) = [V]CST_AYES Then
            End [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRPAY([L]K)
        Endif
    Next [L]K
End ""

Funprog GET_FIRST_SELECTED_BPRINV()
    Local Integer K
    For [L]K = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]K) = [V]CST_AYES Then
            End [M:BSIMTC4]DUDBPRINV([L]K)
        Endif
    Next [L]K
End ""

# DNE X3-53532
Subprog C_DUDPAYCUR(VALEUR)
Variable Decimal VALEUR
    Local Integer I : [L]I = [S]nolign - 1

    # The value must not exceed the oi amount in currency.
    If VALEUR > [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCUR( [L]I )
        Errbox( mess(56,117,1) ) # 'Overpayment not authorized'
        mkstat = 2
    Endif
End


Subprog AM_DUDPAYCUR(VALEUR)
    Variable Decimal VALEUR
    Local Decimal DELTA, DELTASTM
    Local Integer I : [L]I = [S]nolign - 1
    Local Integer STA #angre

    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        [L]DELTA = VALEUR - [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I)

# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
            Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
            Call LEC_TPY_LEG([F:BSIIP]LEG, [F:BSIIP]PAYTYP) From CPTLEC # read payment entry type

            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, DELTA, DELTASTM, [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
            DELTA = DELTASTM
# 2017-08-21 DNE MODIF BEGIN (X3-53026)
            If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = 0
                Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
                Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I), [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I), [L]STA) From
& TRTDEV_SYRA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
            Else
                Raz DELTA
            Endif
# 2017-08-21 DNE MODIF ORIG
#            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC0]BSIPAYSTM([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
# 2017-08-21 DNE MODIF END
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
        Else
            [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC([L]I) = VALEUR
            [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I) = VALEUR
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
            [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        Endif
        #angre end

        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [L]DELTA
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
        [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYLOC( [L]I )
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM( [L]I )
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I)
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I)
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
   Endif
End

Subprog AM_BSIDEPCUR(VALEUR)
Variable Decimal VALEUR
    Local Decimal DELTA, DELTASTM
    Local Integer I : [L]I = [S]nolign - 1
    Local Integer STA #angre

    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        [L]DELTA = VALEUR - [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPCUR([L]I)

# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        #X3-42425
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
            Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
            Call LEC_TPY_LEG([F:BSIIP]LEG, [F:BSIIP]PAYTYP) From CPTLEC # read payment entry type
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, DELTA, DELTASTM, [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
            DELTA = DELTASTM
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
            [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        Else
            [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC([L]I) = VALEUR
            [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM([L]I) = VALEUR
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
            [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        Endif
    #angre end

        [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP += [L]DELTA
        [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
        Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
# 2017-08-21 DNE INSERT BEGIN (X3-53026)
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPLOC( [L]I )
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIDEPSTM( [L]I )
# 2017-08-21 DNE INSERT END
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I)
        Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I)
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
    Endif
End

$UPDATE_NUM
Raz [M:BSIMTC0]NUM
If [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC <> ""
    If [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "O"                                  # open item match
        For [L]J = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1 - 1
            If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]J) = [V]CST_AYES Then
                #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-15 - START
                If len([M:BSIMTC0]NUM)+len([M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM([L]J))+2 <= 250
                  If  [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = ""
                  #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-15 - END
                    #[M:BSIMTC0]NUM += [M:BSIMTC0]DUDNUM([L]J) + chr$(10)
                    [M:BSIMTC0]NUM += [M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM([L]J)
                  #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-15 - START
                  Else
                    [M:BSIMTC0]NUM += "; " + [M:BSIMTC4]DUDNUM([L]J)
                  #JOJAC - X3-119504 - 2019-01-15 - END
                  Endif
                Endif
            Endif
        Next [L]J
    Elsif left$([M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC,1) = "P"           # payment match
        For [L]J = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG - 1
            If [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]J) = [V]CST_AYES Then
                If len([M:BSIMTC0]NUM)+len([M:BSIMTC4]NUM([L]J))+2 <= 250
                  If  [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = ""
                    [M:BSIMTC0]NUM += [M:BSIMTC4]NUM([L]J)
                  Else
                    [M:BSIMTC0]NUM += "; " + [M:BSIMTC4]NUM([L]J)
                  Endif
                Endif
            Endif
        Next [L]J
        # in case of payment match with manual entries > add string "Manual entry" at the end
        If [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "PM" and len([M:BSIMTC0]NUM)+len(mess(266,7703,1))+2 <= 250
          If  [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = ""
            [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = mess(266,7703,1)
          Else
            [M:BSIMTC0]NUM += "; " + mess(266,7703,1)
          Endif
        Endif
    Elsif left$([M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC,1) = "M"           # manual entry
        [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = mess(266,7703,1)            # Manual entry
    Endif
    If [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = "" Then
        [M:BSIMTC0]NUM = mess(265,7703,1)
    Endif
Endif
Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]NUM
Return


########################################################################################################################
$AB3_FACCDE
    Local Integer K, I
    Local Char    OPT(5), VALC1(20), VALC3(20)
    If [L]VALC2 = "" Then
        Return
    Endif

    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = [L]BPSTYP or [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = "*PO" Then
        [L]OPT = "41235"
    Elsif [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = [L]BPCTYP or [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = "*SO"
        [L]OPT = "31245"
    Elsif [L]IPTTYP = 4
        [L]OPT = "2"
    Elsif [M:BSIMTC0]SNS = "1"
        [L]OPT = "21435"
    Else
        [L]OPT = "12345"
    Endif

    For [L]I = 1 To 5
        Case mid$([L]OPT, [L]I, 1)
            When "1" : # Facture client
              Call LECTURE("BIC", [L]VALC2, "") From CONTOBJ
              If fstat = 0 and [F:SIH]GTE = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) Then
                  If [F:SIH]ORIMOD = 3 Then
                      [L]VALC1 = "BIC"
                  Else
                      [L]VALC1 = "SIH" : # Tunnel Reglt -> SIH : GBIDC2 ne peut pas ętre affecté
                  Endif
                  Break
              Endif
            When "2" : # Facture fournisseur
              Call LECTURE("BIS", [L]VALC2, "") From CONTOBJ
              If fstat = 0 and (([L]IPTTYP = 4 and [F:PIH]INVTYP = 5) or ([L]IPTTYP <> 4 and [F:PIH]GTE = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL))) Then
                  If [F:PIH]ORIMOD = 3 Then
                      [L]VALC1 = "BIS"
                  Elsif [F:PIH]ORIMOD = 6
                      [L]VALC1 = "PIH"
                  Endif
                  Break
              Endif
            When "3" : # Commande client
              If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = [L]BPCTYP or [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = "*SO" Then
                  Call LECTURE("SOH", [L]VALC2, "") From CONTOBJ
                  If fstat = 0 Then
                      [L]VALC1 = "SOH" : # Tunnel Reglt -> CCL : GBIDC2 ne peut pas ętre affecté
                      Break
                  Endif
              Endif
            When "4" : # Commande fournisseur
                If GACTX.AFOLD.AMODULE(6) = [V]CST_AYES # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 BEGIN
                    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = [L]BPSTYP or [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL) = "*PO" Then
                        Call LECTURE("POH", [L]VALC2, "") From CONTOBJ
                        If fstat = 0 and [F:POH]POHTYP = 1 Then
                           [L]VALC1 = "POH"
                           Break
                        Endif
                    Endif
                Endif # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 END
            When "5" : # Pičce comptable
                If GACTX.AFOLD.AMODULE(5) = [V]CST_AYES # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 BEGIN
                    Call LECTURE("GAS", [L]VALC2, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL)) From CONTOBJ
                    If fstat = 0 Then
                        [L]VALC1 = "GAS"
                        [L]VALC3 = [M:BSIMTC4]DUDTYP([L]NOL)
                        Break
                    Endif
                Endif # 2017-12-21 DNE X3-68766 END
        Endcase
    Next I
Return

######################################################################################
#angre 190916 Including overpayment
Subprog AM_OVERPAY(VALEUR)
Variable Decimal VALEUR

  [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - ([M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT + VALEUR)
  Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT

End


######################################################################################
Subprog C_OVERPAY(VALEUR)
Variable Decimal VALEUR
  If VALEUR < 0
    Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    mkstat = 2
  Endif
End


######################################################################################
Subprog BSILOG(ACTIVATE)          # Bader: 2016-10-25 X3-1501
Value Integer ACTIVATE
If ACTIVATE = 1
    DOMTCLOG = 1
Else
    DOMTCLOG = 0
Endif
End

######################################################################################
Subprog AM_DUDPAYSTM(VALEUR)

Variable Decimal VALEUR
Local Decimal DELTA
Local Integer I : [L]I = [S]nolign - 1
Local Integer STA

If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL([L]I) = [V]CST_AYES Then
    Call LEC_CPY([F:BSIDUD]CPY) From CPTLEC
    Call LEC_TPY_LEG([F:BSIIP]LEG, [F:BSIIP]PAYTYP) From CPTLEC # read payment entry type
    [L]DELTA = VALEUR - [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYSTM([L]I)

    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
    [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I)
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end

    Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY

    [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT

    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
    If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURAMT([L]I) <> [M:BSIMTC4]DUDCURLOC([L]I)
        If [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) = 0
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, VALEUR, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
            Call CONVERT(GACTX, [M:BSIMTC00]CUR, [F:BSIDUD]CUR, [F:CPY]ACCCUR, [F:TPY]RATTYP, [M:BSIMTC0]VALDAT, [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTLOCBAL([L]I), [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I), [L]STA) From TRTDEV_SYRA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
        Endif
    Else
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR([L]I) = VALEUR
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
        [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I) -= [L]DELTA
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
    Endif

# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader begin update remaining OI amount in screen
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDAMTCURBAL([L]I)
# X3-200184 2020-06-02 Bader end
    Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]DUDPAYCUR( [L]I )
Endif
End


# X3-119483 2019-01-15 Bader begin
######################################################################################
Subprog AM_PAYSEL(VALEUR)
Variable Integer VALEUR
Local Integer I, J, SELECTED

[L]I = [S]nolign - 1
[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]I) = VALEUR

# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader begin to make sure BSISNS has a value other than 0
Read [F:BSIPAY]BSIPAY0 = [M:BSIMTC00]STMCOD;[M:BSIMTC0]LIN;[M:BSIMTC4]LIN1([L]I)
If [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS = 0 : [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS = 1 : Endif
# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader end

[L]SELECTED = find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG-1))     # number of selected payments after change
If VALEUR = [V]CST_AYES Then
# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader begin respect BSISNS when setting selected amount
#    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]BANPAYTPY([L]I)
#    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I) = [M:BSIMTC4]BANPAYTPY([L]I)
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS * [M:BSIMTC4]BANPAYTPY([L]I)
    [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I) = [F:BSIPAY]BSISNS * [M:BSIMTC4]BANPAYTPY([L]I)
# X3-128734 2019-03-18 Bader end
    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT += [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I)       # update total
Else
    If not [L]SELECTED > 0  # no payment selected any longer
        # delete manual entries, if existing
        If !clalev([F:BSIMAN])  Local File BSIMANENT   [BSIMAN]   Endif
        Trbegin [F:BSIMAN]
        Delete [F:BSIMAN] Where STMCOD = [M:BSIMTC0]STMCOD and LIN = [M:BSIMTC0]LIN
        If fstat
            mkstat = 2
            Errbox([F:BSIIMPD]STMCOD + "~" + num$( [F:BSIIMPD]LIN ) - mess(4,7703,1)) # "Transaction cannot be deleted"
            Rollback
            End
        Else
            Commit
        Endif
    Endif
    [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT -= [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I)     # update total
    Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I)
    Raz [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I)
Endif

[M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT = [M:BSIMTC0]AMTCUR - [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT     # update remaining amount
Raz [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
Raz [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY

[M:BSIMTC0]LET = "AM"

# set/reset [M:BSIMTC0]MTCTYP
If [L]SELECTED = 0 Then
    [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = ""
Else
    [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC = "P"
Endif

Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYCUR([L]I)
Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]BSIPAYSTM([L]I)
Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]LET
Affzo [M:BSIMTC0]TYPMTC
Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTAMT
Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]TOTDEP
Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]RSTAMT
Affzo [M:BSIMTC4]OVERPAY
End


$COUNT_PAYMENTS_SELECTED
[L]SELECTED = 0
For [L]J = 0 To [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG - 1
    If [L]I <> [L]J and [M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL([L]J) = [V]CST_AYES Then
        [L]SELECTED = 1
        Break
    Endif
Next [L]J
Return


######################################################################################
$APRES_MODIF
If COUZON = "PAYSEL" or COUZON = "DUDSEL"
    Gosub SETBOUT From GOBJSUB      # enforce correct handling of "Manual entry" button

    Gosub SHOW_HIDE_TOTALS

    If COUZON = "PAYSEL" and find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]PAYSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG-1)) > 0    # number of selected payments after change > 0
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1                                                                # disable open items grid
    Elsif COUZON = "DUDSEL" and find([V]CST_AYES,[M:BSIMTC4]DUDSEL(0..[M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1-1)) > 0    # number of selected open items after change > 0
        Diszo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG                                                                 # disable payments grid
    Else
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG1                                                                # enable open items grid
        Actzo [M:BSIMTC4]NBLIG                                                                 # enable payments grid
    Endif
Endif
Return
# X3-119483 2019-01-15 Bader end

